Package inc.solutions.numerical

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Matrix_Solve_Behavior
    This is an interface that contain only ona method to declare the matrix solving behavior of each possible mathematical method.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Gaussian_Solver_Behavior
    This class implements Matrix Solve Behavior to create a behavior thar solves an matrix equation with Gaussian Elimination.
    LinearSolverDeluxe
    This is a the main class that solves matrix equations.
    Matrix_Inversion_Behavior
    This is a class implements Matrix_Solve_Behavior to create a new behavior to solve equations with Matrix Inverse method.
    NullBehavior
    This is the main behavior of any solver instance.
    Solver
    This is a class that solves equations with its behavior.
